<item>
            <title>[LU-3525] Add / extend Lustre tools to parse rpc_stats and brw_stats.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3525</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Both llstat and llobdstat are great tools for summarizing Lustre /proc data for analysis and plotting, but am not aware of a similar Lustre tool for rpc_stats or brw_stats.  Have found that Collectl parses these files much like ll&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;obd&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;stat parses stats files, but there appears to be an incompatibility (&lt;a href=&quot;http://sourceforge.net/p/collectl/bugs/21/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://sourceforge.net/p/collectl/bugs/21/&lt;/a&gt;) which prevents Collectl from fully parsing rpc_stats.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thus, having a Lustre provided/supported tool to parse these files would seem to be of great benefit to monitoring &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;brw|rpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;_stats files over time.  Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
